column5: Leaving tomorrow and picking up my sister and brother in law in Toronto, and then will be taking our time to be there for Sundays race. My sister and brother in law are flying in from Vancouver. We don't usually get to see them to often, but this will be the third time this year. Gonna have a blast, hope everyone else has a great weekend. Will post some pics when I get back or maybe sooner as most hotels have internet these days.
Awesome Deano, wish I could join you.  Take a picture of Tony for me okay.  Have a blast.  Joey
Have a blast Deano. Another 7 weeks before I go.
We went to the August Michigan race last year. We had a great time. Have fun!!

Deano see you there lol. l will be in the Gordon Stuff like the rest of the world. lol Have a blast and leave the liver at home.
